  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goal: Mainstream primary education in Bangladesh is accessible to children with disability, particularly, irreversibly visually impaired children.
Purpose of Project: Children with disability, particularly, those with visual impairment are studying alongside sighted children in selected mainstream formal primary schools in Sunamganj district and community is empowered to sustain the effort to promote IE. 
Project Objectives: 
Objective # 1. Enrol children with disabilities, including visually impaired children to mainstream primary schools
Objective # 2. Create physical and educational environment for VI children 
Objective # 3. Advocate at local level for inclusive education
Objective # 4: Strengthen organizational and management capacity</narrative>
  </description>
